column6: In order to save a handful of lives, the powerless Stephen Strange has made a decision that will doom far more--and he has no way to undo it. The price Strange and his new apprentice will pay to set things right is incalculable--and will leave Stephen Strange forever changed! Rated T  ...$3.99
column8: | penciller:Tomm Coker | penciller:Emma Rios | writer:Mark Waid
